  "title": "Allure x Fresh Animations",
  "description": "Fresh Animations compatibility patch for the Allure Resource Pack!",
  "body": "<center>\n  <h1><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c311e4e83b8a25e2e32b731abfbce012a3eefc6d.png\" alt=\"Allure x Fresh Animations\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-fresh-animations-support\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/allure-6439754/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p><hr><p><strong>Allure x Fresh Animations</strong> is a simple Resourcepack that adds support for the animations from <strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-animations\">Fresh&nbsp;Animations</a></strong> for <strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack\">Allure</a></strong>.</p><hr>\n<p>Please note that for the pack to work correctly you need to have your packs ordered like this:</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e0336e2ab512d908fadc5aa59998b1928c961abf.png\" alt=\"Allure x Fresh Animations,\\n Fresh Animations,\\n Allure,\\n Default\">\n<hr>\n<p>If you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n<br><br><hr>\n<h1>Other Projects!</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab67244910ef4ab4fca79d7e98f4f7afbe9a75ec.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-emoji-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure Emoji Pack\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/62de9de72ccd55e8a14fd4b637eb9c54dd0fb888.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-3d-plants\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a46651adb88e91abf37823d73fa1b42f66d4b596.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-dark-theme-gui\"><img alt=\"Allure Dark Theme GUI\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f8deee765f891b6ca092c2ae5c120c8ea01c9007.webp\"></a>\n</center>",
